dern media celebrity that now occupies an increasingly prominent place in our contemporary popular culture.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aDaredevilszUnited StatesxHistory. 0aStunt performerszUnited StatesxHistory. 7aHISTORY / United States / General.2bisacsh  aadrenaline junkies.  aadrenaline lovers.  abase jumping.  abooks about daring stunts.  abooks for young adults.  adeath defying stunts explained.  adiscussion books.  aeasy to read.  aengaging.  aevel knievel.  afun books to read.  ahistory of stunts.  ahistory.  ahollywood.  ahow to be a stunt double.  ahow to do a trick.  aincredible humans.  alearning from experts.  aleisure reads.  apage turner.  apopular culture.  aquarantine books.  asky diving.  astart of media.  astunt double history.  astunt pilots.  athrill makers.  avacation reads.  ax games.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z97831106904220 cprintz978052027088640uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052095236240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520952362423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520952362/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY